Homonym Number:  2
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:strategy, theme, platform
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: [Ma. <b>kaupapa</b> strategy, theme, level floor, fleet of ships]  cf. P.M. Ryan Dict. Modern Maori (1995) 89.
